# Migrating fg-gemini's Frontend into fg

## What fg-gemini Has (That fg Doesn't)

All of these are **hand-written** during fg-gemini's development — there are no external downloads, CDN libraries, or third-party design systems to fetch. Everything lives in the repo as [.tsx](file:///C:/Users/kirkm/Projects/fg/packages/web/src/App.tsx) and [.ts](file:///C:/Users/kirkm/Projects/fg/packages/web/vite.config.ts) files using Tailwind utility classes.

