### 3. Mock Data Layer
**Source:** [data/mockData.ts](file:///C:/Users/kirkm/Projects/fg-gemini/packages/web/src/data/mockData.ts)

700-line file containing TypeScript types, mock data arrays, and a simulated API service (`api` object) with localStorage persistence. This provides the entire data layer for the frontend to function without a real backend.

### 4. Icon Library
**npm package:** `lucide-react` (already in fg-gemini's [package.json](file:///C:/Users/kirkm/Projects/fg/package.json))

All icons throughout the UI come from [Lucide](https://lucide.dev/) — an open-source icon set. This is an npm dependency, not downloaded files.

