## Key Differences Between the Two Projects

| Aspect | fg | fg-gemini |
|--------|-----|-----------|
| **Routing** | `react-router-dom` (URL-based) | State-based (useState) |
| **Fonts** | DM Sans + DM Serif Display (Google Fonts CDN) | Inter + system-ui (CSS only) |
| **Primary color** | Green palette (`#22c55e`) | Orange palette (`#ee7a12`) |
| **Icons** | None | `lucide-react` |
| **React version** | 18.x | 19.x |
| **Vite version** | 5.x | 6.x |
| **Pages** | Empty placeholder | 13 full pages |
| **Components** | Empty directory | Full UI library |

