## What You Do NOT Need to Download

- **No external stylesheets** — all styling is Tailwind utility classes written inline
- **No CSS frameworks** — both projects already have Tailwind configured
- **No icon files** — `lucide-react` is an npm package (Step 1)
- **No image assets** — all images are Unsplash URLs and pravatar.cc URLs embedded in the mock data
- **No design tokens** — the UI component library defines its own styles inline
